text: Margaret Gibson (born 4 January 1961) is a Zimbabwean rower. She competed in the women's coxless pair event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Zimbabwean female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Zimbabwe Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
